        <content type="html" xml:base="https://yzzfo.github.io/unity/store/UModeler/ignore-index-en/">&lt;p&gt;Model and Sketch your World in Unity.&lt;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;UModeler&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; provides you with the most convenient environment for low-poly 3D modeling and prototyping within Unity.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;classic.umodeler.com&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Website&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;discussions.unity.com&#x2F;t&#x2F;released-umodeler-x-model-rig-paint-and-ai-texture-within-unity-unity-vsp&#x2F;659243&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Unity Discussions&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; |&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;umodeler.github.io&#x2F;index.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt; Manual&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.tripolygon.com&#x2F;tutorials&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Tutorial Videos&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;discord.gg&#x2F;Pfct3hf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Discord&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.facebook.com&#x2F;umodeler&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Facebook&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; |&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;umodeler.github.io&#x2F;releasenotes.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Release Note&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; |  Contact.Support@umodeler.com&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;THINGS TO KNOW&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li &gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.youtube.com&#x2F;watch?v=xnEjmJA4PAg&amp;list=PLVpxoFqeUjC-D463duAjqmZGy0F0uwGiL&amp;index=1&amp;t=4s&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Watch UModeler Essentials Videos, narrated by Indie Game Hustle&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;&lt;li &gt;Finalist for &quot;Best Development Tool&quot; at Unity Awards 2018&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;&lt;li &gt;Includes the &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;assetstore.unity.com&#x2F;packages&#x2F;3d&#x2F;environments&#x2F;urban&#x2F;the-pastel-town-182014&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;PastelTown&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;-BuiltInRP-UModeler package as a default demo asset&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;&lt;li &gt;Streamlined and reliable Prefab workflow, starting from UModeler version 2.9.18&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;&lt;li &gt;Minimum Unity version required to use UModeler is 2019.4.x&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;&lt;li &gt;UModeler doesn&#x27;t support the runtime API and editing.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;ARTICLES&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li &gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;80.lv&#x2F;articles&#x2F;modeling-moonglow-village-in-unity-with-umodeler&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Modeling Moonglow Village in Unity with UModeler [80.lv]&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;&lt;li &gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;80.lv&#x2F;articles&#x2F;level-design-in-unity-witch-s-cauldron&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Level Design in Unity: Witch’s Cauldron [80.lv]&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;&lt;li &gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;80.lv&#x2F;articles&#x2F;level-design-in-unity-blocking-out-a-cyberpunk-scene-with-umodeler&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Level Design in Unity: Blocking Out a Cyberpunk Scene with UModeler [80.lv]&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;&lt;li &gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;80.lv&#x2F;articles&#x2F;modeling-a-mech-robot-in-unity-with-umodeler&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Modeling a Mech Robot in Unity with UModeler [80.lv]&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;&lt;li &gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;80.lv&#x2F;articles&#x2F;umodeler-for-unity&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;UModeler for Unity [80.lv]&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;1) No need for export &amp;amp; import processes to create your world anymore.&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Edit and manipulate 3D meshes directly within Unity, in the final environment context.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• See shader&#x2F;VFX results instantly whenever you modify a base mesh.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Modify and tweak meshes made with external DCC software (such as Blender, 3ds Max, Maya, etc.) right in Unity.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;2) Sketch-Based 3D Modeling Technique&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Various drawing tools and the PushPull tool allow for intuitive 3D shape creation.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Quickly prototype your level using this feature.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;3) Comprehensive 3D Modeling Tools and UV Editor&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Quickly create 3D assets and levels with nearly 150 versatile tools.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• UModeler features adjustable 3D primitive shapes for added flexibility.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Unwrap any mesh and edit UVs directly in Unity with the built-in UV Editor.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;• &lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;80.lv&#x2F;articles&#x2F;umodeler-adds-a-new-hotspot-texturing-feature&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;New Feature: Hotspot texturing is now available!&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;4) High Compatibility with other Unity Assets&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• &lt;strong&gt;ProBuilder&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;: Smooth conversion of ProBuilder meshes.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• &lt;strong&gt;Polybrush&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;: Seamlessly edit UModeler meshes with Polybrush.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• &lt;strong&gt;Synty Studio&#x27;s 3D Assets&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;: Convert 3D meshes into UModeler and edit them seamlessly.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• &lt;strong&gt;Surforge&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;: Fully compatible with PBR texturing.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• And more&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;5) Extensive Learning Materials and Active Online Communities&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Narrated tutorial videos for both beginners and intermediate users.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Comprehensive &#x27;Timeline&#x27; and &#x27;Full-making&#x27; videos demonstrating 3D asset modeling with UModeler.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Engage with a vibrant community on &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;discord.gg&#x2F;Pfct3hf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Discord&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; and the &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;forum.unity3d.com&#x2F;threads&#x2F;released-umodeler-a-ultimate-and-intuitive-modeler-for-unity.462506&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unity Forum&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;. Ask questions, share insights, or showcase your art.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;6) Who Can Benefit from UModeler?&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Level Designers&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• 3D Modelers&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Concept Artists&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Technical Artists (TAs)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• VFX Artists&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Programmers&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• Indie Game Developers&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;• And more&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;If you want to know the lastest information, visit our blog post: &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;docs.umodeler.com&#x2F;blog&#x2F;umodeler-x-2025-jan-news&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;docs.umodeler.com&#x2F;blog&#x2F;umodeler-x-2025-jan-news&#x2F;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
